### growOperands() {#a692faa915034f2720ea905b7d3cdfa6a}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="void IndirectBrInst::growOperands ()">
growOperands - grow operands - This grows the operand list in response to a push&#95;back style of operation.

This grows the number of ops by 2 times.
